{"'Arrays must have the same length'":"E0","'string notation required for auto precision.'":"E1","INPUT_ERROR":"E2","FINALIZE_ERROR":"E3","'Illegal argument ' + message":"E4","'Invalid data'":"E5","'The amount of data is too big to be stored in a QR Code'":"E6","'\\n' +\n      'The chosen QR Code version cannot contain this amount of data.\\n' +\n      'Minimum version required to store current data is: ' + bestVersion + '.\\n'":"E7","'No input text'":"E8","'Encoder not initialized'":"E9","'\"' + data + '\"' +\n      ' cannot be encoded with mode ' + Mode.toString(mode) +\n      '.\\n Suggested mode is: ' + Mode.toString(bestMode)":"E10","'\"version\" cannot be null or undefined'":"E11","'\"version\" should be in range from 1 to 40'":"E12","'\"toSJISFunc\" is not a valid function.'":"E13","'Invalid QR Code version'":"E14","'FetchError'":"E15","`HTTP error! status: ${response.status}`":"E16","'Invalid JSON response from server'":"E17","'The provider is not valid.'":"E18","msg":"E19","\"Cannot find module '\"+o+\"'\"":"E20","'resolver must be a function'":"E21","'Cannot resolve promise with itself'":"E22","'must be an array'":"E23","\"Cannot call a class as a function\"":"E24","'Failed to get type for BinaryArray'":"E25","'Unkown type: ' + type":"E26","\"Can't call config() after localforage \" + 'has been used.'":"E27","'Database version must be a number.'":"E28","'Custom driver not compliant; see ' + 'https://mozilla.github.io/localForage/#definedriver'":"E29","'Method ' + methodName + ' is not implemented by the current driver'":"E30","'Driver not found.'":"E31","'No available storage method found.'":"E32"}